title: Revelations
info:
REVELATIONS - 6'50


by Iron Maiden - Cover by Malekith
Tracked for "BEST OF THE FANS II" musicdisk

One of my favorite Maiden songs, I first wanted to track it for BOTF 1 but
I didn't have enough good samples to do an "above-average" mod. Then I
found some good metal mods, I asked permission to rip some samples (mainly
solo guitar and drums) and now, here it is...


Clean guitar parts redone with Hybrido's pack. I kept the original samples
'cos i wasn't gonna do the whole module again (something else to do :-))
Original samples by Zack and Betrayer.
